:INFO
Shapes and Thickness Guide
Setting 5 on most machines gives a good thickness for fettuccine and tagliatelle. \
Setting 6 works for pappardelle. Setting 7 gives a near- transparent sheet for ravioli \
or tortellini. For lasagne, setting 6 to 7 works well since the sheet absorbs liquid

